been ruled out by Scotland Yard, but the motive of the blast
remains a mystery.
</P>
<P>
Police said the device appeared to be aimed at harming people,
not property. It was planted next to a supermarket.
</P>
<P>
Hospital sources say two of the most seriously hurt patients
may be blinded because of injuries to the eyes from flying nails
and glass.
</P>
<P>
