<HEADLINE> Fresh Fighting Kills at least 17 Rebels in S.Lanka </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
COLOMBO, April 18 (Xinhua) -- Sri Lankan government troops
Saturday killed at least 17 Liberation Tigers of Tamil Eelam
(LTTE) rebels in the north of the country, the Defense Ministry
announced Sunday.
</P>
<P>
