<P>
In Vaddukoddai West in Jaffna, troops cordoned off a safe house
and killed three rebels who were hiding inside a bunker in the
house. One more rebel was killed in ambush in Periyamadu in
northern Wanni.
</P>
<P>
LTTE rebels have been fighting the Sri Lankan government since
1983 for an independent Tamil homeland in the north and east of
the country. 
</P>
