<HEADLINE> Venezuelan President Offers to Mediate in Colombian Feud </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SANTO DOMINGO, April 17 (Xinhua) -- Venezuelan President Hugo
Chavez said on Saturday that he is willing to mediate between the
guerrillas and the Colombian government.
</P>
